\par <#/>This year, he got Kabarak on the pedestal with his play, }{\i\fs24\lang2057 The Scum}{\fs24\lang2057 , which won seven awards in the national Kenya Schools Drama Festival held in Mombasa in April. <#/>A week and a half ago, the same play was the t
alk of town when the festival winners performed at the Kenya National Theatre. 
