\par <#/>Under his gifted hand, Kasigwa led Kaaga to the drama festival finals in 1983, 1985 and 1986. <#/>In 1985, his play, }{\i\fs24\lang2057 The Trials}{\fs24\lang2057  was the overall winner apart from getting six trophies. <#/>The 1987 entry, }{
\i\fs24\lang2057 Wishful Thinking }{\fs24\lang2057 came second in the same festival. 
