\par }{<#/>}{\fs24\lang2057 Looking at some of the things that take place in their societies, older generations have been known to complain about the manners of the younger generations. 
\par <#/>Ma
nners, we have been told, make the man, and we can of course add that they also make the woman. <#/>This saying means that we judge a person's character by his manners. <#/>If he is of good behaviour we say that he is cultured or refined. <#/>However, if 
