ms to is each morning assaulted when they see who wields authority where they work. 
\par <#/>That situation has led to domestic violence against women as a "disciplinary measure". <#/>As a result of their education and financial security, some women will now no
t docilely accept a beating from their husbands. <#/>Instead they will fight back in some cases, some will even abandon a man who resorts to brawn instead of brain as a means of settling family disputes. 
\par <#/>In addition to all this, there is the exposure that the modern woman has had from feminist movements. <X_>}{\v\fs24\lang2057 <#/>
Although these movements are usually elitist and sometimes militantly misguided, their assertion of women's rights has been in direct proportion to a decline in what is some\-times referred}{\b\v\fs24\lang2057  }{\v\fs24\lang2057 to as}{
