e about, no matter how hard he racked the deeper recesses of his creativity. 
\par <#/>Well, you remember sympathising with Martin and understanding the pain of his predicament: anyone who has been caught up in a no-go creative impasse knows just how much misery it entails. <#/>Ask any scribe working for this paper!
